<H3> <TI>   Serbian Army Deploys Forces Near Pristina </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU2602201594 Tirana TVSH Television Network in Albanian 1900 
GMT 26 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU2602201594 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana TVSH Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Albanian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Kosova Information Center reports of new 
movements of Serbian Army in several centers in Kosova. Dozens 
of trucks have been deployed from a military barracks in 
Prizren. Meanwhile, 10 tanks and some heavy artillery have been 
deployed in Hajvali hills near Prishtina. 
  Serbian Army movements have even been observed in the 
direction of Gjakove. Heavy cannons have also been installed 
near Prizren, while 18 tanks have been deployed in Tumosh, 
Podujeve. Low flights by military planes have become more 
frequent over Prishtina and other cities in Kosova. 

</TEXT>

