<F P=102>  LD2402222294 Bratislava STV 1 Television Network in Slovak 
1730 GMT 24 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2402222294 </F>
<F P=104>  Bratislava STV 1 Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Slovak </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] There are 10.4 billion Slovak korunas [Sk] earmarked 
in the 1994 state budget for the Slovak Defense Ministry. The 
sum is Sk2.2 billion higher than in 1993. However, this year's 
expenditures include payments into the Health Insurance Fund, 
hospital care, and pension insurance, as well as a contribution 
of Sk30 million for Slovakia's top sports and financial support 
of Sk34 million for studies at nonmilitary schools. 

</TEXT>

