<F P=102>  LD2502212794 Warsaw PAP in Polish 1648 GMT 25 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2502212794 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw PAP </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Polish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Warsaw, 25 Feb--The official visit to Poland by 
Ukrainian Foreign Minister Anatoliy Zlenko, scheduled for 28 
February-1 March, has been deferred and will take place at 
another time, the Foreign Ministry Press and Information 
Department reported today. 
  The Foreign Ministry comunique adds that the visit has been 
deferred at the request of Minister Zlenko. A new date has not 
yet been decided upon. 

