<H3> <TI>   Silajdzic, Granic, Zubak Comment </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU0203113694 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in 
Serbo-Croatian 1100 GMT 2 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU0203113694 </F>
<F P=104>  Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Serbo-Croatian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Statements by Bosnia-Herzegovina Prime Minister Haris </F>
Silajdzic, Croatian Foreign Minister Mate Granic, and Kresimir 
Zubak, representative of the Bosnian Croats, in Washington on 2 
March; Silajdzic, Granic, Zubak speak in English with 
superimposed Serbo-Croatian translation -- recorded] 
