<H3> <TI>   Government Adopts 1994 Agriculture Program </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU0103135794 Skopje MILS-NEWS in English 1 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> AU0103135794 </F>
<F P=104>  Skopje MILS-NEWS </F>


