<H3> <TI>   Serb Artillery Kills 11 in Bihac Aid Line </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU0303120494 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in 
Serbo-Croatian 1100 GMT 3 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU0303120494 </F>
<F P=104>  Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Serbo-Croatian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Serb aggression against the free parts of 
Bosnia-Herzegovina is not letting up. Following the tried and 
tested Sarajevo ploy, the criminal [Serb military leader Ratko] 
Mladic's gunners continue to murder civilians. 
  After yesterday's massacre in Bihac, when 11 citizens were 
killed and dozens wounded in a queue for the distribution of 
